t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>893<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>619<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>3,212<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/cbd8f43df3f5398db1f1d365ac553ca22.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shining Slash<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>6<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies in a line.<br>Both this skill\'s critical rate and the critical rate<br>of attack skills in dragon form will be increased<br>by 10% for each buff with a different icon applied<br>to the user.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 507 \\u00d7 4 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,870<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 11,193<br><\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/20cad8e4fa011f9a61e0e16c16dc42ba2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Brilliant Booster<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Greatly increases the modifier applied to the user\'s<br>critical damage, and grants the user a strength amp.<br>After this amp is granted, this skill will not grant it<br>again for 30 seconds.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Skill Energy Required: 3,899<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbCritical Damage +80%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 3)<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength +10%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases strength by 10%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9d2241ad3a4cf58afa2121060c21dc9c2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Light) Above 10 Hits = Shadow Res +10%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Light: <br>reduces shadow damage taken by them by 10%<br>when the combo count is 10 or higher.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/daec86e89dfb95ad45d6f68c08c841752.png\\"><\/span><span>Connecting Call III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases Luca\'s critical rate by 4% for<br>every buff with a different icon applied<br>to him (up to 28%). In addition, applies<br>one of the following buffs to Luca every<br>time one of his attacks is a critical hit:<br>Sylvan Secret Arts, Human Wisdom,<br>and Rokkan Expertise. Each of these buffs<br>increase Luca\'s critical rate by 4% for<br>20 seconds. Only one instance of each<br>buff can be active at the same time. After<br>activating, this ability will not activate again<br>for three seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5cf36e722ea56b427d85b9c405f4302d2.png\\"><\/span><span>Unforgettable Promise III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to curses and poison<br>by 100%. When the user is hit by an attack that<br>would have cursed or poisoned them, their<br>critical rate is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/25ef50e0a0cfce84d2ec98ed78c188702.png\\"><\/span><span>Critical Rate +13%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases critical rate by 13%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1623650400,"prev_article_id":"2256","next_article_id":"2259","image_path":"","update_time":1623299697}}}'